            <title>[SPARK-3103] Fix UTF8 encoding in PySpark saveAsTextFile().</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-3103</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a follow-up JIRA for &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/1914&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/1914&lt;/a&gt;, where Ahir and Davies identified a bug in Python JsonRDD when trying to encode non-ASCII strings into unicode.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The same underlying issue affects saveAsTextFile, so we should apply the same fix there, too, and search for any other code that needs to be updated (and maybe refactor this out into a utility function).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
